data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4-bedroom, 3 full bathroom home with a 2-car garage. This spacious home is perfect for families or anyone who loves to entertain. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a stunning open-concept layout adorned with high ceilings. Natural light pours in through numerous windows, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. A large living room and dining area that flow seamlessly into the updated kitchen. The kitchen boasts NEW stainless-steel appliances, quartz countertops, and plenty of storage space. The master suite has a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. Other features of this home are a large and fenced backyard that's perfect for outdoor entertainment, and plenty of room to play or garden. THIS IS AN ENERGY EFFICIENT HOME WITH RENEWAL ENERGY! to SAVE IN YOUR ELECTRICAL BILL and to contribute to a more sustainable planet. Located in a quiet and friendly neighborhood, this home is just minutes from local schools, parks, and shopping. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful home yours!
